---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---
<div class="py-32 px-4 bg-[#0e1610] relative">
  <div class="layout-content-container max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-20 text-center opacity-0" data-animate="fade-in">
      <h2
        class="font-mono text-primary text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4"
      >
        // TESTIMONIALS
      </h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
        
        Client Endorsements
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:w-1/3 md:pt-10 opacity-0" data-animate="slide-in-up">
        <div
          class="bg-surface-card p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 relative hover:border-primary/20 transition-all"
        >
          <div class="mb-6 text-primary">
            <Icon name="material-symbols:format-quote-outline" class="text-2xl"/>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-base italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Alex built a scalable architecture that handled our 10x growth
            seamlessly. The code quality is exceptional.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-900 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs"
            >
              JS
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">James Sullivan</h5>
              <span class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider"
                >CTO, FinTech Global</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:w-1/3 opacity-0" data-animate="slide-in-up">
        <div
          class="bg-surface-card p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 relative hover:border-primary/20 transition-all bg-gradient-to-b from-white/5 to-transparent"
        >
          <div class="mb-6 text-primary">
            <Icon name="material-symbols:format-quote-outline" class="text-2xl"/>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-base italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Rarely do you find a developer who understands design this well. The
            implementation was pixel-perfect.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-purple-900 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs"
            >
              EL
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Elena Rodriguez</h5>
              <span class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider"
                >Product Lead, EcoApps</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:w-1/3 md:pt-16 opacity-0" data-animate="slide-in-up">
        <div
          class="bg-surface-card p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 relative hover:border-primary/20 transition-all"
        >
          <div class="mb-6 text-primary">
            <Icon name="material-symbols:format-quote-outline" class="text-2xl"/>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-base italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Professional, timely, and innovative. The automated deployment
            pipeline set up saved us countless hours.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-900 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs"
            >
              MK
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Marcus K.</h5>
              <span class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider"
                >Founder, SaaS Co.</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
